description: Removes the specified tags from the specified AWS RoboMaker resource. To remove a tag, specify the tag key. To change the tag value of an existing tag key, use TagResource.

parameters.name: resourceArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the AWS RoboMaker resource you are removing tags.

parameters.name: tagKeys
parameters.description: A map that contains tag keys and tag values that will be unattached from the resource. (string) ---
